# ğŸ® Tic Tac Toe - Solo or Duo

A fun, interactive Tic Tac Toe game built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Play against a smart computer or challenge a friend!

![Tic Tac Toe Game](https://via.placeholder.com/800x400?text=Tic+Tac+Toe+Game)

## âœ¨ Features

### ğŸ¯ Game Modes
- **Single Player** - Play against computer with smart AI
- **Two Player** - Play with a friend on the same device

### ğŸ¤– Smart Computer AI
The computer makes intelligent moves by:
- Trying to win whenever possible
- Blocking the player from winning
- Taking center position first
- Then corners, then sides

